{"tid":1849992,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家如果要係街邊掉口罩既話，麻煩掉之前至少抆斷個兩條繩，避免有人執黎用","createTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:07:38.000Z","uid":66260,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc5f13b3b27b153f96981cd13d99f4d4cd4b2a9","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"fb見到好多人執，懷疑有人想賣二手口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95410e7fe980849be797a5026b79e40c38db3112","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:22:09.000Z","msg":"有筆既話就畫花佢<br />\n有剪刀既話直頭剪爛佢先掉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">處理完記得洗手，口罩收埋好多細菌病毒</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"742aada7583a85da2f4604a2974d5993d2f80678","tid":1849992,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bcc5f13b3b27b153f96981cd13d99f4d4cd4b2a9","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"fb見到好多人執，懷疑有人想賣二手口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"會黐返上去"},{"pid":"89dd67312803a35a8f91647d33a21c2a71288f0f","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"742aada7583a85da2f4604a2974d5993d2f80678","tid":1849992,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bcc5f13b3b27b153f96981cd13d99f4d4cd4b2a9","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"fb見到好多人執，懷疑有人想賣二手口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"會黐返上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"照抆<br />\n總之增加佢地賣二手口罩既成本"},{"pid":"d36d5c74c11c3466b8741a6780e13961bbb9cb2b","tid":1849992,"uid":288673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc5f13b3b27b153f96981cd13d99f4d4cd4b2a9","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"fb見到好多人執，懷疑有人想賣二手口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"真係 CLS"},{"pid":"16e123592623d403a92eb638b380164b7c02007a","tid":1849992,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b002dc8512faed6d48578ae735885abd52a573","tid":1849992,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf4e4bd02b556504ca8d8743fa1e421cb6242f1","tid":1849992,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:34:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0368ad6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=39f007df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=c117b660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=9c8c7083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=83bbe80a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=01664ec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=44feb466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fnpptl%2Ftopics%2Frespirators%2Ffactsheets%2Frespsars.html&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=5dee64ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html</a><br />\nSARS 時期CDC 對N95 同防毒面具嘅指引<br />\n（僅供參考！WARS 嘅傳染性係SARS 嘅一倍以上！！！！）"},{"pid":"51e4abbe956924e5369d450e50639fa3fb88c8c4","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fa29a836f66acc63ded4c0da8a861006757993","tid":1849992,"uid":53695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"我直頭扯爛中間，有時帶返屋企就拎較剪剪爛先，最多洗手消毒較剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fad002edc3cdd98f7307c265026c3c301b2ca2e","tid":1849992,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6879d06e3728ff8b6cf0cdbb6be46642930501a","tid":1849992,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"用袋入 打個結"},{"pid":"d7e7439766ef4bccb1dae7a654a46f0ea1119d12","tid":1849992,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"用過嘅口罩有摺痕 又唔係獨立包裝 請知點賣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42709441a247445e6cfe63fab99afee74b45480b","tid":1849992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T23:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac625e8dc6f08840910c7dfb7823665f8dfb3833"